replies.body: ....umm...you did nothing but walk in and kill him...in no way juked....he used nothing on that clone but a single rocket....did he even have any items? or were you just completely over fed?
he was juked beacuse i was invis and he actually was running away from clone towards me... so he was like wtf and i was like hehe
no....thats not juke...thats flanked. and even then....he didnt really have anywhere else to go...

well i didnt really get the meaning of jukes..
so now i corrected it and now its outplayed...
